data.name: label11.Text
data.value:
In some cases, funds from deposits may ont be available for immediate withdrawal. In that event, you will be notified in writing and advised when the funds will be available.
If your check has two or more endorsements, please present it to a Teller in a Branch.
How are you making a deposit? Please make a selection below.

data.name: labelInstructionEn.Text
data.value:
You will be asked to perform three common transactions on an ATM machine.
These transactions are: 1. Check the balance in your checking account. 2. Transfer 50 dollars from your savings account to your checking account. 3. Withdraw 100 dollars from your checking account.
Press “Continue” when you are ready to continue.

data.name: labelInstructionSp.Text
data.value:
Usted va a completer 3 transacciones communes en el cajero automático.
Las transacciones son: 1. Verificar el saldo de su cuenta de cheques. 2. Transferir 50 dólares de su cuenta de ahorros a su cuenta de cheques. 3. Retirar 100 dólares de su cuenta de cheques.
Oprima “Continuar” cuando estás listo para continuar.
